{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/cookie-sync/","webpackCompilationHash":"90c601cc54f34fcad120","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Blog","author":"Gerard Nguyen","siteUrl":"https://nvanthao.github.io"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"037e0953-1b4f-58c0-8f34-e412135f8fb0","excerpt":"uid is a cookie on .criteo domain that is used to anonymously collect user activities on multiple websites with the purpose of displaying targeted ads. This…","html":"<p><strong>uid</strong> is a cookie on .criteo domain that is used to anonymously collect user activities on multiple websites with the purpose of displaying targeted ads.</p>\n<p>This cookie is set when the first call to Criteo widget server is made\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 335px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8c97f9943e290e7435a701bc8160316e/de5dc/set-uid.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.56716417910448%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"set-uid\"\n        title=\"set-uid\"\n        src=\"/static/8c97f9943e290e7435a701bc8160316e/de5dc/set-uid.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8c97f9943e290e7435a701bc8160316e/cf440/set-uid.png 148w,\n/static/8c97f9943e290e7435a701bc8160316e/d2d38/set-uid.png 295w,\n/static/8c97f9943e290e7435a701bc8160316e/de5dc/set-uid.png 335w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 335px) 100vw, 335px\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Now after some times, let’s go to view our cookie databases.\nIn Linux, for Firefox, you can view this in <strong>~/.mozilla/firefox/$PROFILE_NAME/cookies.sqlite</strong></p>\n<p>If we do below query,</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">SELECT</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> host<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">value</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">FROM</span> moz_cookies\n<span class=\"token keyword\">WHERE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">value</span> <span class=\"token operator\">LIKE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'%e2a2f822-a67a-44ed-99b3-fa83b3b57997%'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>We can see multiple entries with content like our Criteo UID\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7630ea2dbb0e44c6b7307781ea7d5347/d68ed/sync.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 77.24719101123596%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"sync\"\n        title=\"sync\"\n        src=\"/static/7630ea2dbb0e44c6b7307781ea7d5347/b9e4f/sync.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7630ea2dbb0e44c6b7307781ea7d5347/cf440/sync.png 148w,\n/static/7630ea2dbb0e44c6b7307781ea7d5347/d2d38/sync.png 295w,\n/static/7630ea2dbb0e44c6b7307781ea7d5347/b9e4f/sync.png 590w,\n/static/7630ea2dbb0e44c6b7307781ea7d5347/d68ed/sync.png 712w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>This is the basis of Cookie sync, at some point of time in a page, Criteo script will call other publisher networks passing its UID.\nOther networks may drop another cookie with Criteo UID as value and voila, they now can send this data point to Criteo later.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"A quick look at cookie sync","date":"August 13, 2019"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/cookie-sync/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/hello-world/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"I won $54.45 in Powerball!!!","tags":["fun"]}},"next":null}}}